=== CLEANED FILE 1: A Voice Episode Forty_One 07 December 2025_cleaned.vtt ===

WEBVTT

00:00:28.736 --> 00:00:31.498
Welcome to the Ocean Studio and our

00:00:31.559 --> 00:00:33.841
weekend edition of the Yada Yahowah blog.

00:00:34.261 --> 00:00:35.601
I’m your host, Craig Winn.

00:00:36.262 --> 00:00:37.482
When we sit out here,

00:00:37.844 --> 00:00:40.786
hovered above the Caribbean Sea to bring

00:00:40.805 --> 00:00:41.926
this program to you,

00:00:42.487 --> 00:00:44.828
it typically means that we’re going to be

00:00:44.889 --> 00:00:48.871
delving into the lyrics that our King,

00:00:49.231 --> 00:00:49.851
our Savior,

00:00:50.072 --> 00:00:53.835
the very Son of God wrote on behalf

00:00:54.075 --> 00:00:56.237
of His Father, Yahowah.

00:00:57.158 --> 00:01:00.103
And we shall do that very thing again

00:01:00.143 --> 00:01:00.682
today.

00:01:01.564 --> 00:01:02.524
Dowd is His name.

00:01:02.566 --> 00:01:03.567
He is the Messiah.

00:01:03.627 --> 00:01:04.768
He is the Chosen One.

00:01:04.808 --> 00:01:05.769
He is our Shepherd.

00:01:06.569 --> 00:01:08.091
He is the Shamaym,

00:01:08.292 --> 00:01:11.635
the great branch that represents the Tree

00:01:11.676 --> 00:01:13.477
of Lives that grew in the center of

00:01:13.518 --> 00:01:13.959
the Garden.

00:01:14.878 --> 00:01:16.698
Dowd is the man who has already lived

00:01:16.819 --> 00:01:18.760
two of his three lives.

00:01:19.019 --> 00:01:22.302
He was king three thousand years ago in

00:01:22.421 --> 00:01:24.703
Israel, uniting the nation,

00:01:24.743 --> 00:01:26.243
defending God’s people,

00:01:26.885 --> 00:01:29.826
capturing its heart as Jerusalem,

00:01:30.326 --> 00:01:31.688
acquiring the Temple Mount.

00:01:32.468 --> 00:01:35.909
He wrote over one hundred verses—

00:01:37.456 --> 00:01:39.358
Psalms and Proverbs.

00:01:40.599 --> 00:01:43.180
One of the most prolific authors of the

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:45.763
ancient world, maybe the most prolific.

00:01:46.183 --> 00:01:48.043
He was a prophet of the first order.

00:01:48.844 --> 00:01:50.165
In his second of three lives,

00:01:50.225 --> 00:01:52.388
he came to fulfill Pesach, Matsah,

00:01:52.427 --> 00:01:52.927
and Bikuwrym,

00:01:53.147 --> 00:01:56.210
as he described in his own words.

00:01:56.590 --> 00:01:59.894
Read the twenty-second Mizmowr Psalm,

00:01:59.933 --> 00:02:01.814
the eighty-eighth, the hundred and third.

00:02:02.215 --> 00:02:03.555
Read any one of the first thirty.

00:02:03.677 --> 00:02:04.576
They all speak of it.

00:02:04.856 --> 00:02:05.477
Read what Yahowsha‘, the great prophet,

00:02:05.972 --> 00:02:07.855
had to say about him throughout his text.

00:02:07.875 --> 00:02:11.737
Clearly,

00:02:12.799 --> 00:02:13.199
Dowd is the one who fulfilled Pesach,

00:02:13.618 --> 00:02:15.381
Matsah, and Bikuwrym.

00:02:15.441 --> 00:02:16.161
He is the one who is the actual

00:02:16.181 --> 00:02:18.223
man that the myth of Jesus was created

00:02:18.242 --> 00:02:21.265
to rob.

00:02:21.725 --> 00:02:22.246
He is the most interesting man in the

00:02:23.227 --> 00:02:27.151
world.

00:02:27.170 --> 00:02:27.510
And I hope that as we proceed,

00:02:29.231 --> 00:02:31.114
and we are going to begin again in

00:02:31.234 --> 00:02:32.914
the sixth psalm or Mizmowr,

00:02:32.955 --> 00:02:34.657
that you are listening because it is Dowd

00:02:35.693 --> 00:02:38.816
who will come back in his third of

00:02:38.836 --> 00:02:41.197
three lives.

00:02:41.277 --> 00:02:41.957
He is returning as our King.

00:02:42.497 --> 00:02:43.959
Yahowah is explicit in describing this in

00:02:44.098 --> 00:02:47.121
the Eighty-ninth Mizmowr,

00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:48.641
probably the most important piece of

00:02:49.302 --> 00:02:51.223
literature ever written.

00:02:51.264 --> 00:02:52.243
It was described by Yahowah Himself on

00:02:52.724 --> 00:02:55.086
behalf of His beloved son, Dowd.

00:02:55.126 --> 00:02:57.008
And in it,

00:02:57.027 --> 00:02:59.068
He says that Dowd is returning.

00:02:59.128 --> 00:03:00.870
He will return on the Day of

00:03:01.334 --> 00:03:03.217
Reconciliation.

00:03:03.276 --> 00:03:04.258
That will be at sunset in Jerusalem,

00:03:04.299 --> 00:03:06.622
the second of October,

00:03:06.663 --> 00:03:08.665
2033.

00:03:09.247 --> 00:03:10.508
And it will be possible because of

00:03:11.850 --> 00:03:14.716
everything that happens

00:03:14.876 --> 00:03:15.717
ten days before that time.

00:03:16.498 --> 00:03:19.721
The greatest show on Earth will usher in

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:24.223
a remnant of Yisra’elites, even Gowym,

00:03:24.584 --> 00:03:27.406
who will be prepared to witness his

00:03:27.925 --> 00:03:30.568
arrival with Yahowah.

00:03:30.627 --> 00:03:31.868
And we’re told when that occurs that Dowd

00:03:32.389 --> 00:03:35.151
will be ‘Elyown.

00:03:35.170 --> 00:03:36.271
He will be the very influence of Yahowah

00:03:37.391 --> 00:03:39.794
in our presence.

00:03:40.354 --> 00:03:41.055
And his seat of honor, his throne,

00:03:41.814 --> 00:03:45.236
if you will,

00:03:45.276 --> 00:03:45.677
will be as brilliant as the sun because

00:03:46.561 --> 00:03:48.521
it is Kipurym,

00:03:49.282 --> 00:03:50.423
it’s the Mercy Seat of the Ark of

00:03:50.502 --> 00:03:53.163
the Covenant.

00:03:53.204 --> 00:03:54.524
So this is what we’re working toward.

00:03:54.963 --> 00:03:56.745
It’s just eight years from now.

00:03:56.805 --> 00:03:58.466
And it was three thousand years ago that

00:03:59.086 --> 00:04:01.826
Dowd scribed these words that affirm much

00:04:01.947 --> 00:04:06.248
of what I have just shared with you.

00:04:06.269 --> 00:04:07.628
It begins with Yahowah’s name.

00:04:08.509 --> 00:04:10.871
Dowd is God’s beloved son.

00:04:12.170 --> 00:04:13.771
He knew his Father’s name,

00:04:14.542 --> 00:04:15.581
you should know it as well.

00:04:15.822 --> 00:04:16.822
It is not difficult to pronounce.

00:04:17.483 --> 00:04:19.103
All you need really is to be aware

00:04:19.182 --> 00:04:22.543
of two Hebrew words and you can pronounce

00:04:22.624 --> 00:04:25.624
it and recognize that every one of the

00:04:25.663 --> 00:04:30.605
some eight thousand words and names and

00:04:31.005 --> 00:04:35.266
titles throughout the Hebrew text of the

00:04:35.307 --> 00:04:38.187
Torah,

00:04:38.247 --> 00:04:38.567
prophets, and writings are pronounceable.

00:04:38.607 --> 00:04:41.908
To say that there is one that isn’t

00:04:42.711 --> 00:04:45.072
pronounceable is ludicrous,

00:04:45.112 --> 00:04:46.291
particularly since that one is woven into

00:04:46.331 --> 00:04:48.952
so many other names.

00:04:49.033 --> 00:04:50.213
For example,

00:04:50.314 --> 00:04:50.814
I mentioned the prophet Isaiah.

00:04:50.853 --> 00:04:53.314
His actual name is Yahowsha‘.

00:04:53.355 --> 00:04:56.375
Yahowsha‘ would be one of those that has

00:04:56.547 --> 00:04:59.489
Yahowah’s name.

00:05:00.317 --> 00:05:03.418
That is Mosheh’s successor.

00:05:03.699 --> 00:05:04.478
He is the son of Nun,

00:05:05.038 --> 00:05:08.300
the Eternal One.

00:05:08.380 --> 00:05:10.360
Yahowsha‘ is Isaiah’s name.

00:05:10.540 --> 00:05:11.961
Both names mean the same thing.

00:05:13.257 --> 00:05:15.757
They just put the Ya’oh on either side

00:05:16.697 --> 00:05:18.458
of yasha‘, which is salvation.

00:05:18.478 --> 00:05:22.259
So it means that Yahowah saves or salvation

00:05:22.459 --> 00:05:25.559
is from Yahowah.

00:05:25.718 --> 00:05:29.079
But all you have to do is look

00:05:29.339 --> 00:05:30.220
at two words: hayah.

00:05:30.860 --> 00:05:32.480
And I say hayah because God explained to

00:05:32.500 --> 00:05:34.380
Mosheh that His name was based on the

00:05:35.420 --> 00:05:37.641
verb hayah.

00:05:37.680 --> 00:05:39.461
When written in the first person, I was,

00:05:39.502 --> 00:05:40.021
I am, and I will be.

00:05:41.497 --> 00:05:43.737
It is hey, yowd, hey,

00:05:43.877 --> 00:05:45.517
which therefore explains the pronunciation

00:05:46.838 --> 00:05:48.718
of three of the four letters in Yahowah’s

00:05:48.778 --> 00:05:52.038
name.

00:05:52.139 --> 00:05:54.019
The only one left to deduce is the

00:05:54.079 --> 00:05:54.360
wah,

00:05:54.939 --> 00:05:58.279
and all you have to do is look

00:05:58.379 --> 00:05:58.761
at the word that no one doubts its

00:05:59.021 --> 00:06:00.901
pronunciation: Towrah.

00:06:00.961 --> 00:06:03.081
The “oh” sound,

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:04.382
the vowel sound in Towrah comes from the

00:06:05.141 --> 00:06:06.002
wah.

00:06:06.101 --> 00:06:09.463
Even the heh at the end of Towrah

00:06:09.603 --> 00:06:09.843
is reproduced in its spelling as well.

00:06:11.541 --> 00:06:13.783
Towrah is written with a wah and a

00:06:13.923 --> 00:06:17.305
heh.

00:06:18.067 --> 00:06:22.709
And so we can also look at shalowm,

00:06:22.769 --> 00:06:23.110
probably the most commonly repeated word

00:06:23.911 --> 00:06:26.913
among Hebrew speakers.

00:06:26.952 --> 00:06:29.714
The “oh” sound in shalowm is also from

00:06:30.735 --> 00:06:32.598
the wah.

00:06:33.218 --> 00:06:36.560
It isn’t difficult.

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.281
So Yahowah.

00:06:39.283 --> 00:06:39.822
I just,

00:06:41.673 --> 00:06:44.574
I’m sorry that I’m going to interrupt this

00:06:45.214 --> 00:06:46.776
for a moment.

00:06:46.795 --> 00:06:47.276
And among Jews,

00:06:49.896 --> 00:06:51.278
there is a complete avoidance of Yahowah’s

00:06:52.038 --> 00:06:58.302
name.

00:06:58.341 --> 00:06:58.541
And this comes from the threat and the

00:06:59.622 --> 00:07:03.464
control that rabbis have over the culture.

00:07:04.264 --> 00:07:07.607
The greatest enemy of Jews for the past

00:07:09.081 --> 00:07:12.925
two thousand years have been rabbis.

00:07:12.966 --> 00:07:14.687
They are the ones who erased Yahowah’s

00:07:15.588 --> 00:07:18.110
name.

00:07:18.190 --> 00:07:18.471
Yahowah’s name is not found anywhere in the

00:07:19.732 --> 00:07:22.055
Talmud, not found in the Zohar.

00:07:22.095 --> 00:07:24.937
They’ve completely written Yahowah’s name

00:07:25.158 --> 00:07:27.459
out of His own revelations when they

00:07:27.540 --> 00:07:30.382
share words from the Towrah,

00:07:32.589 --> 00:07:34.372
they replace Yahowah’s name with ‘Adonai,

00:07:34.432 --> 00:07:37.334
which is Satan’s title.

00:07:37.374 --> 00:07:38.535
It means the Lord.

00:07:38.555 --> 00:07:39.295
And so the deprivation of knowing Yahowah’s

00:07:40.836 --> 00:07:44.639
name, since it was erased by the rabbis,

00:07:44.699 --> 00:07:47.401
is one of the greatest crimes ever

00:07:48.281 --> 00:07:50.343
committed.

00:07:50.384 --> 00:07:50.783
Second only to the crime of erasing

00:07:52.586 --> 00:07:55.108
Yahowah’s name so that His people don’t

00:07:55.148 --> 00:07:57.709
know it is disavowing

00:07:57.790 --> 00:08:01.833
everything that Yahowah’s beloved son,

00:08:02.608 --> 00:08:05.170
Dowd, our Savior, the Messiah and King,

00:08:05.410 --> 00:08:08.411
represents.

00:08:08.471 --> 00:08:09.112
Which is why so many Yisra’elites and Jews

00:08:09.692 --> 00:08:12.754
are awaiting the arrival of a nameless

00:08:12.935 --> 00:08:15.235
Mashyach.

00:08:15.375 --> 00:08:16.096
Because quite frankly,

00:08:16.617 --> 00:08:17.596
they don’t know that the returning Mashyach

00:08:18.137 --> 00:08:20.338
is Dowd.

00:08:20.399 --> 00:08:20.838
They do not know that Dowd fulfilled

00:08:21.160 --> 00:08:22.920
Pesach, Matsah,

00:08:22.980 --> 00:08:23.761
and Bikuwrym in his second of three lives.

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:26.002
They don’t know that it is Dowd who

00:08:26.562 --> 00:08:28.043
is returning as King.

00:08:28.084 --> 00:08:29.264
They don’t even know the timeline.

00:08:29.725 --> 00:08:31.125
So they’re unaware that he is going to

00:08:31.584 --> 00:08:33.325
return on the second of October in 2033.

00:08:33.384 --> 00:08:37.609
That’s one of the reasons why Yahowah has

00:08:37.649 --> 00:08:38.269
asked me to speak to you.

00:08:39.149 --> 00:08:41.030
So, Yahowah,

00:08:41.131 --> 00:08:43.052
You consistently prove Your case through

00:08:43.974 --> 00:08:44.573
me with pervasive and persuasive arguments

00:08:46.855 --> 00:08:51.239
which vindicate me

00:08:51.278 --> 00:08:56.403
and acquit through me,

00:08:57.124 --> 00:08:58.125
thereby eliminating everything displeasing

00:08:59.559 --> 00:09:01.581
and disagreeable.

00:09:05.706 --> 00:09:09.532
I realize that we spent an hour in

00:09:10.332 --> 00:09:11.214
our last program from the Ocean Studio on

00:09:12.075 --> 00:09:14.437
this one statement.

00:09:14.498 --> 00:09:17.380
And I can promise you,

00:09:17.421 --> 00:09:18.201
we’re going to spend less time on it

00:09:18.945 --> 00:09:20.285
this time.

00:09:20.306 --> 00:09:21.885
We’re going to move on past it,

00:09:21.986 --> 00:09:22.366
but it is so profoundly important.

00:09:22.407 --> 00:09:23.606
So affirming of everything that I have

00:09:24.107 --> 00:09:26.129
come to know and share that I want

00:09:26.729 --> 00:09:28.429
to reiterate it for you.

00:09:28.470 --> 00:09:31.890
The fact of the matter is that not

00:09:31.971 --> 00:09:34.011
only is Yahowah God’s name,

00:09:34.251 --> 00:09:37.374
the first person to reintroduce it after

00:09:37.453 --> 00:09:41.716
two thousand five hundred years of it not

00:09:41.755 --> 00:09:45.337
being spoken or known.

00:09:46.547 --> 00:09:49.489
Here’s the man that you’re looking at now

00:09:49.528 --> 00:09:50.789
who is speaking to you.

00:09:51.929 --> 00:09:53.571
Yahowah refers to me as Yada.

00:09:53.591 --> 00:09:54.672
My name is Craig Winn.

00:09:55.591 --> 00:09:57.634
I am the author of these books that

00:09:58.374 --> 00:09:59.495
you see off my left shoulder.

00:10:00.514 --> 00:10:03.616
Thirty-five in total.

00:10:03.636 --> 00:10:05.719
Twenty-five thousand pages of translations

00:10:07.379 --> 00:10:09.000
and analysis of God’s testimony.

00:10:09.061 --> 00:10:13.702
It has become the tree of knowledge in

00:10:13.722 --> 00:10:16.144
our world.

00:10:18.263 --> 00:10:21.124
So God wants you to know His name.

00:10:21.203 --> 00:10:21.703
And it is in these books entitled

00:10:22.504 --> 00:10:26.264
appropriately Yada Yahowah.

00:10:27.024 --> 00:10:29.284
Yada means to know.

00:10:29.325 --> 00:10:30.926
It is also the name that Yahowah has

00:10:31.466 --> 00:10:32.546
chosen for me.

00:10:32.826 --> 00:10:35.187
Yada Yahowah—to know Yahowah.

00:10:35.226 --> 00:10:36.047
And it is essential.

00:10:37.547 --> 00:10:39.006
You cannot return to God.

00:10:41.307 --> 00:10:42.087
You cannot enter Heaven.

00:10:42.628 --> 00:10:45.269
You cannot have a relationship with Him

00:10:45.849 --> 00:10:46.808
until you know, love, appreciate,

00:10:48.018 --> 00:10:50.679
pronounce, share, accept,

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:55.163
and celebrate Yahowah’s name.

00:20:22.891 --> 00:20:24.672
the fulfillment of Pesach,

00:20:24.912 --> 00:20:27.432
his body anyway.

00:20:27.452 --> 00:20:29.074
He allowed his soul to go into She’owl

00:20:30.272 --> 00:20:31.817
carrying our guilt to perfect us.

00:20:32.417 --> 00:20:33.941
And then he fulfilled Bikuwrym,

00:20:34.021 --> 00:20:38.010
Firstborn Children, as the Bikowr,

00:20:38.050 --> 00:20:39.493
Firstborn Son of God.

00:20:39.986 --> 00:20:41.807
So Dowd engaged Bikuwrym.

00:20:41.826 --> 00:20:42.346
He was the one who wanted to work

00:20:42.406 --> 00:20:44.887
with Yahowah.

00:20:44.948 --> 00:20:46.769
He was the one who listened to Yahowah.

00:20:46.788 --> 00:20:47.568
He was the one who responded

00:20:47.669 --> 00:20:49.950
appropriately.

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:52.951
He was the student who became the teacher.

00:20:52.990 --> 00:20:54.510
He was the man who did the thing

00:20:54.770 --> 00:20:56.932
that God’s most interested in.

00:20:57.011 --> 00:20:58.292
Yes, Dowd was not perfect.

00:20:58.353 --> 00:21:00.012
He made mistakes.

00:21:00.334 --> 00:21:01.673
He stumbled and he fell.

00:21:02.114 --> 00:21:03.335
But every time he did,

00:21:03.954 --> 00:21:06.935
he learned his lesson.

00:21:08.856 --> 00:21:10.337
He corrected his mistake and he moved on.

00:21:10.978 --> 00:21:13.499
He got back up.

00:21:13.538 --> 00:21:14.298
God knew that this is a man that

00:21:14.338 --> 00:21:15.338
He could depend on,

00:21:15.558 --> 00:21:17.819
that He could rely on,

00:21:18.140 --> 00:21:19.381
that He could go explore the universe with

00:21:21.642 --> 00:21:23.122
and not be worried about.

00:21:23.162 --> 00:21:25.143
And He knew that he would love the

00:21:25.182 --> 00:21:25.823
experience and that they would enjoy their

00:21:26.502 --> 00:21:27.084
time together.

00:21:27.124 --> 00:21:30.244
You see,

00:21:30.305 --> 00:21:31.625
God is the answer to the fall of

00:21:31.664 --> 00:21:35.906
man.

00:21:35.946 --> 00:21:36.567
He’s the man that stood back up to

00:21:38.544 --> 00:21:41.445
walk with Yahowah.

00:21:41.486 --> 00:21:42.027
And so the case is consistently proven

00:21:42.047 --> 00:21:46.789
through Dowd.

00:21:46.890 --> 00:21:48.570
And God provides pervasive arguments which

00:21:48.672 --> 00:21:51.232
vindicate not only Dowd,

00:21:51.272 --> 00:21:52.574
proving that Dowd is the very Son of

00:21:52.594 --> 00:21:53.855
God, that he is the Chosen One,

00:21:53.875 --> 00:21:54.836
that he is our Messiah,

00:21:55.596 --> 00:21:57.317
that he is our King,

00:21:57.377 --> 00:21:58.558
that he is our Savior,

00:21:58.778 --> 00:22:00.800
that he is our Shepherd,

00:22:00.820 --> 00:22:02.442
that he is the Tree of Lives that

00:22:02.721 --> 00:22:06.224
was planted in the midst of that garden

00:22:06.305 --> 00:22:08.006
long ago.

00:22:08.663 --> 00:22:09.663
He is the one

00:22:09.942 --> 00:22:12.503
that God vindicated.

00:22:12.584 --> 00:22:14.203
The whole Eighty-ninth Mizmowr exists to

00:22:14.243 --> 00:22:15.684
vindicate Dowd,

00:22:15.744 --> 00:22:18.144
to explain that Dowd is all of these

00:22:20.006 --> 00:22:20.945
things, and that he is returning.

00:22:21.905 --> 00:22:23.646
But even more than that,

00:22:23.707 --> 00:22:24.067
