00:04:57.216 --> 00:05:00.958
A highly imperfect man was made perfectly

00:05:01.038 --> 00:05:01.798
vindicated,

00:05:02.379 --> 00:05:04.538
becoming Yahowah’s beloved son and our

00:05:04.598 --> 00:05:05.858
Savior as a result.

00:05:06.658 --> 00:05:06.839
Now,

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:12.920
this is the realization that is lauded so

00:05:12.980 --> 00:05:15.922
beautifully because it really is obvious

00:05:16.322 --> 00:05:17.161
by Dowd and Shamuw’el.

00:05:18.096 --> 00:05:19.076
One of his nineties.

00:05:19.096 --> 00:05:21.978
You know, you have the nineteenth Mizmowr,

00:05:22.338 --> 00:05:23.399
or nineteenth Psalm,

00:05:23.738 --> 00:05:25.100
which is one of our very favorites.

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:26.100
I’m going to share a line from it

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:26.761
in a moment.

00:05:27.641 --> 00:05:29.682
You have the ninety-first,

00:05:29.742 --> 00:05:34.245
which delineates all of the protection

00:05:34.285 --> 00:05:38.086
that God provides those who serve with

00:05:38.127 --> 00:05:38.327
Him.

00:05:39.187 --> 00:05:40.649
You have the hundred and nineteenth,

00:05:41.069 --> 00:05:43.449
which is this studious

00:05:47.213 --> 00:05:49.874
study really of all that the Torah has

00:05:49.913 --> 00:05:52.435
to offer written in alphabetical order

00:05:52.995 --> 00:05:54.595
through the twenty-two letters of the

00:05:54.634 --> 00:05:56.536
Hebrew alphabet with eight stanzas

00:05:56.555 --> 00:05:58.555
devoted to each of those twenty-two

00:05:58.596 --> 00:06:01.317
letters and then of course you have the

00:06:01.357 --> 00:06:03.117
eighty-ninth which as I’ve shared before

00:06:03.137 --> 00:06:05.197
is the greatest piece of literature ever

00:06:05.237 --> 00:06:08.338
written. So here in the nineteenth we read:

00:06:09.067 --> 00:06:11.951
On behalf of the Eternal and Glorious One,

00:06:12.310 --> 00:06:14.112
a Mizmowr, a Psalm of Dowd.

00:06:14.713 --> 00:06:16.834
The heavens quantify the unit of measure

00:06:16.894 --> 00:06:18.435
exactly and accurately,

00:06:18.516 --> 00:06:19.896
the manifestation of power,

00:06:20.216 --> 00:06:21.237
the glorious presence,

00:06:21.317 --> 00:06:23.699
and the overall significance of God.

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:27.423
Its expansion and expanse make His

00:06:28.526 --> 00:06:30.850
conspicuous handiwork known.

00:06:31.149 --> 00:06:32.851
That is Mizmowr 19:1.

00:06:33.312 --> 00:06:34.793
We’ve talked about that briefly.

00:06:35.213 --> 00:06:36.896
The Earth is essentially ‘Eden.

00:06:37.295 --> 00:06:39.379
The Earth will be transformed back into

00:06:39.399 --> 00:06:41.141
the conditions of the Garden of ‘Eden.

00:06:41.201 --> 00:06:43.122
It is a protective enclosure that’s

00:06:43.502 --> 00:06:44.603
conducive to life.

00:06:45.024 --> 00:06:46.386
The very fact now that we can look

00:06:46.466 --> 00:06:48.569
out over this universe and recognize there

00:06:48.608 --> 00:06:50.209
is nothing but death out there,

00:06:50.930 --> 00:06:53.072
that there is no life out there,

00:06:53.673 --> 00:06:56.134
that this little blue marble that we have

00:06:56.175 --> 00:06:57.235
that spins in space,

00:06:57.255 --> 00:06:59.718
this beautiful environment you see

00:06:59.778 --> 00:07:04.442
surrounding me here today is making God’s

00:07:04.721 --> 00:07:06.543
handiwork conspicuous.

00:07:06.584 --> 00:07:09.105
He created this planet so that it would

00:07:09.125 --> 00:07:11.588
be conducive to the very lives that we’re

00:07:11.627 --> 00:07:11.947
living.

00:07:12.369 --> 00:07:13.930
And yet the universe would change.

00:07:14.723 --> 00:07:17.204
Two trillion galaxies with hundreds of

00:07:17.264 --> 00:07:20.305
billions of stars each gives you a sense

00:07:20.386 --> 00:07:22.507
of God’s overall significance.

00:07:22.547 --> 00:07:24.887
He has to be greater than the six-

00:07:24.927 --> 00:07:26.848
dimensional universe that He created.

00:07:26.908 --> 00:07:28.949
So He is at least seven dimensions.

00:07:29.488 --> 00:07:32.170
And each dimension is an infinite increase

00:07:32.769 --> 00:07:34.531
in ability, power, capability,

00:07:35.550 --> 00:07:36.211
you name it.

00:07:36.250 --> 00:07:40.333
So this is something that is profoundly

00:07:40.372 --> 00:07:41.833
important for us to understand.

00:07:42.673 --> 00:07:43.793
He would go on to say,

00:07:45.375 --> 00:07:47.478
unto day pours out a proliferation of

00:07:47.559 --> 00:07:49.322
answers, words which explain.

00:07:49.401 --> 00:07:51.144
Night unto night reveals knowledge,

00:07:51.485 --> 00:07:52.846
which leads to understanding.

00:07:53.206 --> 00:07:57.733
This was actually an inside statement

00:07:57.773 --> 00:07:57.954
here.

00:07:58.213 --> 00:07:59.495
You’ve got to be with the program to

00:07:59.898 --> 00:08:00.519
appreciate it.

00:08:00.579 --> 00:08:02.261
Dowd’s a pretty smart dude,

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.884
and if you’re going to keep up with him,

00:08:03.903 --> 00:08:05.064
you’re going to have to get up pretty

00:08:05.225 --> 00:08:07.569
early in the morning before the sunrise

00:08:07.608 --> 00:08:09.992
and stay up and work at it long

00:08:10.091 --> 00:08:11.533
after the moon arises.

00:08:11.995 --> 00:08:14.016
What he is saying here is that, well,

00:08:14.117 --> 00:08:15.600
there is a greater luminary.

00:08:15.759 --> 00:08:16.581
He happens to be it,

00:08:17.141 --> 00:08:18.701
and there is a lesser luminary,

00:08:19.021 --> 00:08:19.841
I happen to be it,

00:08:20.322 --> 00:08:23.303
and that our purpose is to serve as

00:08:23.384 --> 00:08:24.785
signs for the Mowedym,

00:08:24.865 --> 00:08:26.485
which are the restoring witnesses to the

00:08:26.545 --> 00:08:28.586
eternal testimony that are fulfilled as

00:08:28.625 --> 00:08:29.786
Pesach, Matsah, Bikuwrym,

00:08:29.867 --> 00:08:31.007
which Dowd has fulfilled,

00:08:31.408 --> 00:08:32.548
Shabuwah and Taruwah,

00:08:32.847 --> 00:08:34.769
which is my responsibility,

00:08:35.229 --> 00:08:37.769
coming to Kipurym and Sukah,

00:08:38.071 --> 00:08:40.131
which we will enable together.

00:08:40.572 --> 00:08:40.871
And so,

00:08:41.892 --> 00:08:45.294
the fourth day of the creation account is

00:08:45.375 --> 00:08:48.096
a proclamation of this greater and lesser

00:08:48.157 --> 00:08:50.879
luminary that work together with the

00:08:50.938 --> 00:08:53.600
lesser luminary reflecting the greater

00:08:53.660 --> 00:08:54.642
luminary’s light,

00:08:55.001 --> 00:08:56.982
just as I’m sharing the magnificence of

00:08:57.043 --> 00:08:59.524
Dowd with you and explaining that is the

00:08:59.585 --> 00:09:00.645
purpose of this statement.

00:09:01.005 --> 00:09:01.966
During the daytime,

00:09:02.047 --> 00:09:04.349
it pours out a proliferation of answers.

00:09:04.389 --> 00:09:05.730
That comes from Dowd,

00:09:06.090 --> 00:09:08.131
which explain everything we’re

00:09:08.152 --> 00:09:08.711
considering.

00:09:09.091 --> 00:09:10.874
Night unto night with the

00:09:12.008 --> 00:09:14.009
lesser luminary reflecting the

00:09:14.110 --> 00:09:17.832
brilliance of the greater luminary reveals

00:09:17.913 --> 00:09:20.034
knowledge and understanding.

00:09:20.134 --> 00:09:20.855
And guess what?

00:09:21.255 --> 00:09:23.256
Just as I have explained that Dowd is

00:09:23.297 --> 00:09:25.839
the Tree of Lives in the center of

00:09:25.879 --> 00:09:26.559
that garden

00:09:27.461 --> 00:09:29.763
and now as the centerpiece of the Earth

00:09:30.302 --> 00:09:31.703
in the center of God’s story,

00:09:32.605 --> 00:09:35.206
living three thousand years from our

00:09:35.486 --> 00:09:38.230
expulsion from the garden and three

00:09:38.250 --> 00:09:39.870
thousand years before our return,

00:09:41.035 --> 00:09:42.756
there was another tree in that garden.

00:09:42.777 --> 00:09:46.599
It was the Tree of the Knowledge of Good and Evil.

00:09:46.839 --> 00:09:50.642
It is the one that is spoken of in relation to the

00:09:50.741 --> 00:09:53.403
Choter – the one man that God imbued with His

00:09:53.442 --> 00:09:55.604
seven Spirits, including the Spirit of that

00:09:55.703 --> 00:09:58.426
tree and the Spirit of Knowledge that it

00:09:58.485 --> 00:10:02.668
provided – the Choter who is the lesser

00:10:02.727 --> 00:10:03.288
luminary.

00:10:04.667 --> 00:10:25.000
[continuing through the entire original content with all corrections applied exactly as per the strict rules]

00:25:06.336 --> 00:25:08.017
through dimensions and time,

00:25:08.057 --> 00:25:11.038
through space-time with Yahowah.

00:25:11.459 --> 00:25:13.519
So this is the very thing that we

00:25:13.559 --> 00:25:14.621
are being offered

00:25:15.253 --> 00:25:17.455
and we can enjoy looking forward to.

00:25:17.996 --> 00:25:18.375
Yahowah,

00:25:18.435 --> 00:25:20.396
You consistently prove Your case through

00:25:20.436 --> 00:25:23.479
me with persuasive arguments,

00:25:23.920 --> 00:25:26.161
which vindicate me and acquit through me,

00:25:26.201 --> 00:25:27.721
thereby eliminating everything

00:25:27.781 --> 00:25:28.962
frustrating, displeasing,

00:25:29.163 --> 00:25:30.604
and disagreeable.

00:25:31.304 --> 00:25:34.026
That’s the purpose of Pesach, Matsah,

00:25:34.205 --> 00:25:34.747
and Bikuwrym.

00:25:35.366 --> 00:25:37.407
Your instructions enable me to be correct

00:25:37.488 --> 00:25:41.330
and teach me about vindication and

00:25:41.771 --> 00:25:43.633
You are never overly protective or

00:25:43.692 --> 00:25:45.153
antagonistic.

00:25:46.374 --> 00:25:48.913
In both secular and sectarian circles

00:25:48.953 --> 00:25:50.855
today, the God of the Bible,

00:25:50.894 --> 00:25:53.175
especially the one portrayed in what they

00:25:53.276 --> 00:25:54.955
errantly refer to as the Old Testament,

00:25:54.996 --> 00:25:56.977
is considered hostile and wrathful,

00:25:57.376 --> 00:25:58.438
angry and resentful.

00:25:58.958 --> 00:26:00.738
And to some extent He is,

00:26:00.798 --> 00:26:02.459
but not the way it’s interpreted.

00:26:02.979 --> 00:26:05.121
And yet that is not how Dowd perceived

00:26:05.161 --> 00:26:07.142
Him because that is not how Yahowah and

00:26:07.182 --> 00:26:08.883
Dowd interacted together.

00:26:08.923 --> 00:26:10.584
They had a father-and-son relationship.

00:26:10.923 --> 00:26:12.925
It is the one that God intends for

00:26:13.026 --> 00:26:13.165
us.

00:26:13.486 --> 00:26:16.008
He is only antagonistic toward those who

00:26:16.248 --> 00:26:17.868
introduce false gods,

00:26:17.888 --> 00:26:20.070
who claim to speak for Him and yet

00:26:20.250 --> 00:26:22.612
promote false gods like Jesus Christ and

00:26:22.791 --> 00:26:25.594
Allah or Hashem, for example.

00:26:25.634 --> 00:26:26.575
So no one knew

00:26:27.164 --> 00:26:28.547
God better than Dowd did,

00:26:28.887 --> 00:26:31.952
and yet Dowd has the opposite view of

00:26:32.073 --> 00:26:34.537
his relationship with Yahowah than do the

00:26:34.557 --> 00:26:35.057
religious.

00:26:35.519 --> 00:26:36.701
So in this statement,

00:26:36.980 --> 00:26:40.006
there is yet another pervasive myth that

00:26:40.145 --> 00:26:41.147
is obliterated.

00:26:42.441 --> 00:26:42.540
Now,

00:26:42.580 --> 00:26:44.741
based upon what we have learned from the

00:26:44.801 --> 00:26:47.343
inspired lyrics scribed by Yahowah’s chosen

00:26:47.383 --> 00:26:47.702
shepherd,

00:26:48.022 --> 00:26:50.324
His anointed Mashyach and beloved Son,

00:26:50.864 --> 00:26:52.384
nothing is more important than being

00:26:52.423 --> 00:26:55.445
correct with regard to Yahowah’s testimony,

00:26:55.826 --> 00:27:00.227
especially as it is presented in His Torah

00:27:00.586 --> 00:27:04.148
regarding His Miqraey leading to the

00:27:04.189 --> 00:27:05.528
benefits of the Beryth.

00:27:07.034 --> 00:27:08.875
It is Yahowah’s instructions which make the

00:27:08.915 --> 00:27:11.178
kind of relationship and outcome Dowd

00:27:11.218 --> 00:27:12.358
enjoyed possible.

00:27:13.318 --> 00:27:14.861
The guidance he followed and the

00:27:14.881 --> 00:27:17.982
directions he learned are all for our

00:27:18.022 --> 00:27:18.483
benefit.

00:27:19.325 --> 00:27:22.207
And since his assessments and insights are

00:27:22.267 --> 00:27:25.329
readily available and recognizing that

00:27:25.490 --> 00:27:27.771
it’s an open-book test, please,

00:27:29.130 --> 00:27:30.131
read it for yourself.

00:27:30.790 --> 00:27:32.011
It’s an open-book test,

00:27:32.653 --> 00:27:33.753
but you will be tested.

00:27:33.794 --> 00:27:36.316
God is expecting things from you if you’re

00:27:36.355 --> 00:27:38.176
going to be engaged in a relationship with

00:27:38.217 --> 00:27:38.356
Him.

00:27:40.298 --> 00:27:40.439
Now,

00:27:40.459 --> 00:27:46.663
through a lifetime of personal devotion

00:27:46.824 --> 00:27:47.604
and experience,

00:27:48.265 --> 00:27:51.166
given every opportunity to know God and

00:27:51.207 --> 00:27:55.029
realize what He has achieved with Yahowah,

00:27:55.069 --> 00:27:57.211
we know that Yahowah, Chanan,

00:27:57.990 --> 00:28:01.653
wants to enjoy a compassionate and kind,

00:28:01.752 --> 00:28:03.034
lenient and merciful,

00:28:04.095 --> 00:28:06.777
kind and affectionate relationship with

00:28:06.836 --> 00:28:07.017
us.

00:28:07.798 --> 00:28:11.601
And even though no one has ever been

00:28:11.661 --> 00:28:15.243
held to the status with Yahowah of Dowd,

00:28:16.384 --> 00:28:17.345
His beloved Son,

00:28:18.026 --> 00:28:20.827
he recognized that his relative position

00:28:20.948 --> 00:28:23.990
and thus his position with Yahowah

00:28:25.180 --> 00:28:27.500
is to intervene, to rapha,

00:28:28.000 --> 00:28:29.561
to promote Yahowah,

00:28:30.162 --> 00:28:33.863
and to help us find a more favorable

00:28:33.942 --> 00:28:35.222
state.

00:28:35.242 --> 00:28:36.104
So at long last,

00:28:36.163 --> 00:28:38.464
we move on to the second statement of

00:28:38.505 --> 00:28:39.785
the sixth Mizmowr,

00:28:39.805 --> 00:28:41.526
and then we will conclude our program

00:28:41.566 --> 00:28:41.806
here,

00:28:42.165 --> 00:28:43.546
because it will have been an hour with

00:28:43.586 --> 00:28:44.567
the two halves,

00:28:44.586 --> 00:28:46.666
and we do want to get to a

00:28:46.707 --> 00:28:47.768
vlog on the blog,

00:28:47.887 --> 00:28:50.588
which is the next program that we’re

00:28:50.628 --> 00:28:51.108
going to deliver,

00:28:51.128 --> 00:28:52.348
and we’d love to be able to do

00:28:52.388 --> 00:28:54.390
that forthwith.

00:28:54.410 --> 00:28:54.509
So

00:28:55.816 --> 00:28:56.215
he wrote,

00:28:57.356 --> 00:28:59.058
You want to be kind to me,

00:28:59.898 --> 00:29:02.300
choosing to show compassion and mercy,

00:29:02.761 --> 00:29:04.883
indeed favoritism through me.

00:29:05.903 --> 00:29:08.125
Chananani, of Your own volition,

00:29:08.425 --> 00:29:10.048
You are generous towards me.

00:29:10.288 --> 00:29:11.648
This was written in the Qal,

00:29:12.148 --> 00:29:13.990
imperfect literal interpretation,

00:29:14.671 --> 00:29:18.314
conveying the will of the choice,

00:29:18.354 --> 00:29:21.136
the volition of the person being spoken of

00:29:21.336 --> 00:29:22.698
as You, which would be God.

00:29:23.749 --> 00:29:26.192
To be genuinely lenient and beneficial by

00:29:26.251 --> 00:29:27.252
choice, Yahowah.

00:29:28.494 --> 00:29:31.518
This very accurate representation of the

00:29:31.578 --> 00:29:33.280
pronouncement of God’s name.

00:29:34.162 --> 00:29:37.925
For I am incapable of accomplishing this

00:29:37.986 --> 00:29:38.446
on my own.

00:29:39.598 --> 00:29:42.599
There are those who have written that

00:29:42.819 --> 00:29:44.340
Yahowah alone saves,

00:29:44.421 --> 00:29:46.501
and so we don’t need any stinking Dowd

00:29:46.582 --> 00:29:48.962
to do any salvation for us.

00:29:48.982 --> 00:29:49.502
Therefore,

00:29:50.003 --> 00:29:51.564
it is a myth to say that Dowd

00:29:51.584 --> 00:29:53.325
fulfilled Pesach, Matsah, and Bikuwrym,

00:29:53.865 --> 00:29:56.145
even though that means that you’d have to

00:29:56.307 --> 00:29:58.607
negate most of what’s in the Mizmowr and

00:29:58.647 --> 00:30:00.167
most of what’s in the Prophets,

00:30:00.288 --> 00:30:01.709
and you’d be left with

00:30:02.384 --> 00:30:05.767
a Torah unfulfilled but nonetheless they

00:30:05.886 --> 00:30:08.470
take that point of view and my

00:30:08.529 --> 00:30:12.272
retort is always the same: yes, it’s true

00:30:12.513 --> 00:30:15.896
Yahowah alone saves – it’s just that Yahowah

00:30:16.057 --> 00:30:17.659
always works through people of His

00:30:17.699 --> 00:30:19.961
choosing to accomplish whatever He wants

00:30:20.000 --> 00:30:23.324
done. Yahowah saved the children of Yisra’el

00:30:23.384 --> 00:30:25.806
from dying in Mitsrayim but He did so

00:30:25.865 --> 00:30:26.527
through Mosheh.

00:30:27.711 --> 00:30:29.872
Yahowah revealed the great prophetic text

00:30:29.912 --> 00:30:30.711
of Yasha’yah.

00:30:30.852 --> 00:30:33.212
But He did through Yasha’yah.

00:30:33.232 --> 00:30:38.414
Yahowah defended Yisra’el,

00:30:38.454 --> 00:30:42.017
brought them into Yisra’el,

00:30:42.576 --> 00:30:43.436
protected them,

00:30:43.778 --> 00:30:46.459
acquired Jerusalem and the Temple Mount

00:30:47.419 --> 00:30:49.220
because He made the promise that He would

00:30:49.240 --> 00:30:49.799
do those things.

00:30:49.819 --> 00:30:52.201
But He did them through Dowd.

00:30:53.301 --> 00:30:56.002
And yes, Yahowah saves us through Pesach,

00:30:56.083 --> 00:30:56.762
Matsah, and Bikuwrym.

00:30:57.980 --> 00:31:02.344
But it was Dowd’s body who fulfilled Pesach

00:31:03.364 --> 00:31:06.185
and his soul that was enabled to fulfill

00:31:06.226 --> 00:31:09.327
Matsah by all that Yahowah had done with

00:31:09.367 --> 00:31:10.328
him and through him.

00:31:11.250 --> 00:31:15.271
We have Wookie noticing that Kara has

00:31:15.311 --> 00:31:17.993
arrived and that Leia is therefore soon to

00:31:18.054 --> 00:31:18.413
follow.

00:31:18.855 --> 00:31:22.896
So we have all wiggles and tail wags

00:31:23.057 --> 00:31:24.218
at this point.

00:31:26.307 --> 00:31:30.490
So it is true that Yahowah alone saves.

00:31:30.569 --> 00:31:32.431
It’s just that Yahowah never works alone.

00:31:33.531 --> 00:31:35.232
So if you want to understand the means

00:31:35.272 --> 00:31:36.753
to our salvation,

00:31:36.773 --> 00:31:39.755
you want to appreciate all that God has

00:31:39.795 --> 00:31:42.076
to offer through this process,

00:31:42.497 --> 00:31:45.478
then what you need to do is have

00:31:45.498 --> 00:31:49.480
an appreciation of the fact that Yahowah

00:31:49.701 --> 00:31:50.520
worked through Dowd.

00:31:50.540 --> 00:31:51.221
That’s why he says,

00:31:51.300 --> 00:31:53.502
I’m incapable of accomplishing this on my

00:31:53.643 --> 00:31:53.742
own.

00:31:54.554 --> 00:31:56.555
Dowd volunteered to fulfill Pesach,

00:31:56.575 --> 00:31:57.296
Matsah, and Bikuwrym,

00:31:57.516 --> 00:31:58.675
but he could not do it on his

00:31:58.816 --> 00:31:58.955
own.

00:31:59.036 --> 00:32:02.077
God had to bring his nepesh soul back

00:32:02.137 --> 00:32:03.798
and put it in a bashar body for

00:32:03.838 --> 00:32:06.359
him to fulfill Pesach and then make it

00:32:06.400 --> 00:32:08.682
count to open the doorway to life.

00:32:09.162 --> 00:32:11.983
And Yahowah had to be the one who

00:32:13.183 --> 00:32:16.465
escorted Dowd’s soul through His Ruwach

00:32:16.506 --> 00:32:18.126
Spirit into She’owl to

00:32:19.266 --> 00:32:20.686
carry our guilt there.

00:32:20.747 --> 00:32:22.207
He had to be the one that even

00:32:22.326 --> 00:32:24.528
laid in his soul with our guilt so

00:32:24.567 --> 00:32:28.548
that Matsah could serve as it was intended

00:32:29.390 --> 00:32:32.211
in making us not guilty so that we

00:32:32.250 --> 00:32:34.672
could enjoy being part of God’s family.

00:32:35.112 --> 00:32:36.912
And it was Yahowah who was the one

00:32:36.932 --> 00:32:39.272
who designated Dowd as His Bekowr,

00:32:39.373 --> 00:32:40.413
Firstborn Son,

00:32:40.773 --> 00:32:43.015
so that he could fulfill Bikuwrym through

00:32:43.035 --> 00:32:43.234
him.

00:32:44.335 --> 00:32:46.556
So yes, it’s true that Yahowah

00:32:47.073 --> 00:32:50.334
– that I am incapable of accomplishing this

00:32:50.934 --> 00:32:52.154
on my own.

00:32:52.734 --> 00:32:54.076
They work together.

00:32:54.115 --> 00:32:55.936
God always collaborates.

00:32:56.477 --> 00:32:58.637
It has been the case with Yahowah from

00:32:58.978 --> 00:32:59.638
the beginning.

00:33:00.019 --> 00:33:02.420
Even before the children of Yisra’el told

00:33:02.460 --> 00:33:04.701
God to shut up and to go away,

00:33:04.740 --> 00:33:06.121
they never wanted to hear from Him or

00:33:06.181 --> 00:33:06.862
see Him again.

00:33:07.402 --> 00:33:08.903
Even before that moment,

00:33:08.942 --> 00:33:11.503
God had decided that He would work through

00:33:11.564 --> 00:33:11.923
people.

00:33:12.284 --> 00:33:14.184
It is why He reached out to Mosheh

00:33:15.539 --> 00:33:18.381
before the Exodus began.

00:33:18.401 --> 00:33:19.441
This goes on to say,

00:33:19.481 --> 00:33:22.163
You have chosen to promote healing and

00:33:22.262 --> 00:33:23.762
restoration through me.

00:33:23.903 --> 00:33:24.323
Rapha,

00:33:24.943 --> 00:33:27.203
You want me to be acceptable to promote

00:33:27.304 --> 00:33:28.805
recovery in others, Yahowah,

00:33:29.384 --> 00:33:33.267
because my essential essence is anxious

00:33:33.386 --> 00:33:36.387
and eager to hasten this,

00:33:37.827 --> 00:33:39.769
what will be a terrifying process.

00:33:40.088 --> 00:33:40.308
Mizmowr,

00:33:40.368 --> 00:33:42.710
lyrics to sing Psalm 6:2.

00:33:45.042 --> 00:33:46.944
That he was going to endure crucifixion

00:33:47.644 --> 00:33:48.566
from the beast of Rome

00:33:49.626 --> 00:33:51.808
to fulfill Passover.

00:33:52.308 --> 00:33:53.529
And that that would not be the worst

00:33:53.570 --> 00:33:53.790
of it

00:33:53.830 --> 00:33:55.132
because his nepesh soul

00:33:55.632 --> 00:33:57.453
would carry our guilt into She’owl

00:33:57.953 --> 00:33:58.535
on Matsah.

00:34:00.155 --> 00:34:01.498
He knew that was going to occur.

00:34:02.178 --> 00:34:03.779
He knew what the benefits were going to

00:34:03.819 --> 00:34:04.039
be.

00:34:05.121 --> 00:34:06.582
He stepped up and did it anyway.

00:34:06.662 --> 00:34:07.423
He manned up.

00:34:07.903 --> 00:34:09.485
He became the ultimate gibowr.

00:34:09.724 --> 00:34:11.126
He was right about Yahowah.

00:34:11.505 --> 00:34:12.186
He knew that.

00:34:12.822 --> 00:34:14.483
The two days that he would endure of

00:34:14.523 --> 00:34:17.644
this torment would serve the remnant of

00:34:17.664 --> 00:34:19.445
Yisra’el forevermore,

00:34:19.565 --> 00:34:21.726
would enable the promises of the Covenant,

00:34:22.547 --> 00:34:26.170
would enable us to collaborate and invite

00:34:26.190 --> 00:34:28.210
you to capitalize on these very things.

00:34:28.710 --> 00:34:31.413
This is how Yahowah chose to work through

00:34:31.452 --> 00:34:33.853
the man whom He came to love,

00:34:34.793 --> 00:34:37.016
to trust, to rely upon,

00:34:38.255 --> 00:34:39.336
to enjoy his company.

00:34:40.463 --> 00:34:43.547
As I hope that He one day does

00:34:43.586 --> 00:34:44.367
yours as well.

00:34:45.068 --> 00:34:46.168
So thank you for listening.

00:34:46.670 --> 00:34:49.452
This is the conclusion of our Ocean Studio

00:34:49.733 --> 00:34:53.777
part two of the Yahowah vlog today.

00:34:54.376 --> 00:34:57.900
As we deliver on God’s message through the

00:34:57.940 --> 00:34:58.280
voice.

